cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper focuses on using machine learning techniques to predict solar irradiance, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence and machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also involves time series analysis, which falls under the category of signal processing (cs.SI). The use of regression techniques such as neural networks and regression trees also suggests the sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
